name: "Crash, burn, die !"
description:
Photography of things that do not exist for more than a fleeting moment, undefined by time and space. 
Nonsensical environments where logic and reality do not hold sway. Accidental imagery relying more on chance, whim, obtuse thought patterns and often a sense of play. The relentless search for the lightness and darkness within life.

That day I nearly died while answering a Facebook post. Never drink and drive, never text either.
